Uses of Class
org.jgum.category.Category

  • Packages that use Category 
    Package Description
    org.jgum  
    org.jgum.category
    Classes in this package model categories and their properties.
    org.jgum.category.named
    Classes in this package model a named categorization as a hierarchical graph of categories.
    org.jgum.category.type
    Classes in this package model a type categorization as a hierarchical graph of categories.
    org.jgum.strategy
    Classes in this package provides support for associating strategies, following the chain of responsibility pattern, with hierarchical categories.
    org.jgum.traversal
    Classes in this package implement common routines for traversing a category graph.
